Package domain.block

Class SurroundingBlock

java.lang.Object
domain.block.Block
domain.block.SequenceBlock
domain.block.SurroundingBlock
Direct Known Subclasses:
SingleSurroundingBlock
public abstract class SurroundingBlock
extends SequenceBlock
An abstract class of SurroundingBlocks that extends SequenceBlock. It has a conditionblock and a bodyblock.

4.0
